view.name: Building and Safety Temporary Special Event (TSE) Permits
view.description: Temporary Special Events being held within the City of Los Angeles are required to be inspected and approved by the Department of Building and Safety. A Temporary Special Event permit application is filed with the Department of Building and Safety as a prerequisite for inspection.
